{"tid":1168920,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"替代Android系統 「華為鴻蒙」已註冊商標","createTime":"2019-05-24T04:27:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-24T06:08:19.000Z","uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"cf9bbb42493b763f8c0172eb74d8e89610a85def","tid":1168920,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T04:27:46.000Z","msg":"替代Android系統 「華為鴻蒙」已註冊商標<br />\n<br />\n2019-05-24<br />\n<br />\n大陸國家智慧財產權局商標局網站顯示，華為已申請註冊「華為鴻蒙」商標。<br />\n<br />\n「華為鴻蒙」申請日期是2018年8月24日，註冊公告日期是2019年5月14日，專用權限期是從2019年5月14日到2029年5月13日。<br />\n<br />\nGoogle終止與華為部分業務往來，華為智慧手機用戶將來可能無法更新Android作業系統，第一財經報導，華為從2012年開始規劃自家操作系統「鴻蒙」，意在成為Android系統的替代品。<br />\n<br />\n「鴻蒙」系統主要是基於Linux所開發。Linux是一套開源的操作系統，即是人人均可使用，過去主要用於伺服器。<br />\n<br />\n有關「鴻蒙」作業系統，據消息指出，此作業系統已對Linux大量優化（已開源），並用於華為手機（安全部分）。在此之前，華為推出自研EROFS超級檔案系統，僅是基於華為方舟編譯器開發的應用，但有專家認為，就能讓Android 系統性能提升數倍來看，底層整合了EROFS和方舟編譯器的華為鴻蒙系統，已具備了一定實力。<br />\n<br />\n但市場分析認為，Android系統幾乎占手機市場99%市占率，大量軟體都是基於Android開發，涵蓋生活各個層面。<span style=\"color: red;\">一個新的系統基本上沒有軟體支持，再強也只算是一部功能機，現在通行的在Android上用的軟體，數量之多簡直難以計算，要軟體商重新開發另一套去支持「鴻蒙」，幾乎是不可能的任務。</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/7333/3831571?from=udn-ch1_breaknews-1-0-news\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F7333%2F3831571%3Ffrom%3Dudn-ch1_breaknews-1-0-news&d=jM2msIR27xdcbllsFNIWhD4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=4d15b4b3\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/7333/3831571?from=udn-ch1_breaknews-1-0-news</a>"},{"pid":"6f7a05295a6a6ed3ffd75359f8856230a6cd0a27","tid":1168920,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T04:29:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cf30ba8bcd0984235133f5c7a0430016fff2e8e","tid":1168920,"uid":41914,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T04:31:15.000Z","msg":"唔使問一定食到APK, 如果唔係真係等執笠/鎖國"},{"pid":"cfaed1d56f015f9b1915490fa47a0f308173737b","tid":1168920,"uid":186997,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T04:31:16.000Z","msg":"到頭來所謂自主燃發都仲係拎Linux嚟改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d017e5ab7e4b4cd97d68e97325cc3dbfc16a7070","tid":1168920,"uid":158613,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"quote":{"pid":"cfaed1d56f015f9b1915490fa47a0f308173737b","tid":1168920,"uid":186997,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T04:31:16.000Z","msg":"到頭來所謂自主燃發都仲係拎Linux嚟改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T04:35:29.000Z","msg":"唔係可以點？唔通用Java自己寫一個？<br />\n等你寫好之後，Java 再告鳩你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67f57598ece4c5515ec9916684278c0fda9dd133","tid":1168920,"uid":41116,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T04:40:38.000Z","msg":"huawei homo"},{"pid":"c7b46ed4a57a0146d1d345bef8ef98e30fdc5b7f","tid":1168920,"uid":164477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T04:42:41.000Z","msg":"開post請鴻蒙developer先"},{"pid":"c858c21d7ebae5bda12ac19051ce5a84431e90f6","tid":1168920,"uid":20473,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T04:42:57.000Z","msg":"有幾難？<br />\n中國政府規定所有android app 要出鴻蒙版"},{"pid":"2e98bfadf8c2fdfb6091ba43c52219086445c6ea","tid":1168920,"uid":34409,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T04:43:10.000Z","msg":"真係俾蒙撚用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49a136c0894e7e8e4330f67c29d2efb719954073","tid":1168920,"uid":96406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T04:44:27.000Z","msg":"乜撚叫鴻蒙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8428495b5a97d3bdd22032ad960b91c70bf74f55","tid":1168920,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c858c21d7ebae5bda12ac19051ce5a84431e90f6","tid":1168920,"uid":20473,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime"